A Dedicated Host Reservation  is a commitment that : 
* You want a specific  Dedicated host type 
* For 1 year or 3 years
* You pay ALL Upfrnot / Partial Upfront / No Upfront
* AWS gives you up to 70 to 75 per discounts

- YOu keep the host
- You can launch any number of allowed instances on the host 
- Nobody else shares the physical server 

Why do we need dedicated host reservation : 
>> Dedicated host is billed On-Demand  -> Extremly expensive  
With  reservation 
>> You get big cost saving 
